@page "/aboutUs"

<MudContainer>
    <!-- Main content -->
    <div class="main-content">
        <div class="about-section">
            <MudText Typo="Typo.h4" Class="about-heading">About Us</MudText>
            <MudText Typo="Typo.body1" Class="about-text">
                Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed aliquam nunc ut diam scelerisque, nec interdum turpis fringilla.
                Nulla quis ex sed lacus convallis hendrerit vel nec justo. Maecenas viverra ultrices odio, eget suscipit elit posuere ac.
                Phasellus malesuada ligula vel libero vehicula tincidunt. Fusce efficitur erat nec sem consequat, id faucibus quam auctor.
            </MudText>
        </div>

        <div class="image-gallery">
            <MudCard Class="gallery-item">
                <MudSkeleton Variant="SkeletonVariant.CardMedia" />
                <div class="overlay"></div>
            </MudCard>
            <MudCard Class="gallery-item">
                <MudSkeleton Variant="SkeletonVariant.CardMedia" />
                <div class="overlay"></div>
            </MudCard>
            <MudCard Class="gallery-item">
                <MudSkeleton Variant="SkeletonVariant.CardMedia" />
                <div class="overlay"></div>
            </MudCard>
        </div>
    </div>
</MudContainer>

<style>
    .toolbar-content {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .logo {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    .main-content {
        padding: 32px;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .about-section {
        margin-bottom: 64px;
    }

    .about-heading {
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #007bff; /* Blue color */
    }

    .about-text {
        color: #333; /* Dark gray color */
    }

    .image-gallery {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
        gap: 16px;
    }

    .gallery-item {
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .overlay {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background-color: rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.5); /* Cyan-ish overlay */
        opacity: 0;
        transition: opacity 0.3s ease-in-out;
    }

    .gallery-item:hover .overlay {
        opacity: 1;
    }
</style>
